The first semantic level: training and increasing the mobility of the spine in areas of the chest and the neck. Especially useful for those over 40 or who lead a sedentary lifestyle. Exercise helps to improve blood circulation, brain nutrition, treatment of headaches. </P>
<p> Second level of meaning: it improves the circulation of <i> qi </i> through the energy channels, helps it to rise from the feet up through the spine, opening biologically active points on the body as it moves. </p>
<p> The third semantic level: you have to get used to the image of a crane drinking water from a lake. Then, having entered the deep state of qigong, after a certain training you can understand the language of birds.